{"tid":1017255,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《皓鑭傳》：反派做主角","createTime":"2019-02-11T10:17:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-11T10:35:46.000Z","uid":160973,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9603b0019b9e91312e5c50f3d543223c123c8eb7","tid":1017255,"uid":160973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T10:17:07.000Z","msg":"農曆新年，《皓鑭傳》開播，進入五線劇四線外購的局面，《開心速遞》成為唯一的無綫代表，要等月尾的《福爾摩師奶》才有新無綫劇看。《皓鑭傳》集數極長至六十二集，預料播到四月初。《延禧攻略》七十集也沒有觀眾嫌長，可惜，縱然是原班人馬的姊妹作，卻未必可以延續《延禧》的奇蹟。<br />\n<br />\n值得留意的是《皓鑭傳》並不是《延禧》成功後才製作的真正姊妹作。《延禧》去年七月開播，但《皓鑭傳》四月已經煞科。事實是，于正當日開拍《延禧》和《皓鑭傳》是要借大劇《如懿傳》和《巴清傳》的東風，一個清朝，一個戰國。<br />\n<br />\n《皓鑭傳》講述女主角李皓鑭身為趙國御史之女落難，被聶遠飾演的商人呂不韋看中，把她當成爭奪權力的籌碼，而皓鑭為了改變命運配合，最後嫁給秦國質子嬴異人，也就是歷史中呂不韋和異人奇貨可居的故事。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2SpfNMJ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2SpfNMJ&d=hKO5vKCyTOC8%2FV9T1xBu18jWZIlHEnPb%2Ft7norCwxRo%3D&h=786d8916\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2SpfNMJ</a>"},{"pid":"924dbdce9d3cc415be27558ddd809e902e76629a","tid":1017255,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T10:18:37.000Z","msg":"有冇淫婦趙雅？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8588587b36872e28344719a188cdbcc14e168eee","tid":1017255,"uid":3441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"924dbdce9d3cc415be27558ddd809e902e76629a","tid":1017255,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T10:18:37.000Z","msg":"有冇淫婦趙雅？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T10:25:59.000Z","msg":"有，不過唔淫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a258f4f24bb03c84e462d80ca3aaca9ef7649326","tid":1017255,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8588587b36872e28344719a188cdbcc14e168eee","tid":1017255,"uid":3441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"924dbdce9d3cc415be27558ddd809e902e76629a","tid":1017255,"uid":81113,"like":1,"d